data.description: Amazing 3/2.5 Santa Fe minutes from Ventana CC with premium views and an elevated corner lot make this home simply one of a kind. Inside this home is a true SW gem with Mexican tile floors, high ceilings, tongue and groove ceilings with natural wood beams at foyer make this home aesthetically on point for those with an architectural love of the Southwest. Tiled baths, kitchen counters, and kiva fireplaces add to the SW sophistication this home offers. Outside this home shines with multiple backyards perfect for dogs or gardeners. Large patios complemented in natural rough saw post and beams enhance the Tucson lifestyle all winter long. This home shows better in person than online and its priced to sell so schedule you showing today!
